POLIOMYELITIS UPDATE (17): PAKISTAN WPV1, GLOBAL CVDPV2 (ACUTE FLACCID PARALYSIS DEMOCRATIC REPUBLIC OF THE CONGO, NIGERIA, SOMALIA), CVDPV3 (ENVIRONMENTAL SAMPLES ISRAEL, PALESTINIAN AUTHORITY)
